Class Menu

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.Menu

  • public class Menu
extends java.lang.Object
    Menu class, represents restaurant menu. Contains 2 ArrrayList, 1 storing individual MenuItem objects and one storing PromotionalPackage Objects.
